WEBVTT

00:05:28.067 --> 00:05:30.956
you would see this incredible,
beautiful, 23-inch arm.

00:05:30.980 --> 00:05:33.583
(Laughter)

00:05:33.607 --> 00:05:35.686
It's pretty, ain't it? It's cut up.

00:05:36.641 --> 00:05:39.568
No fat on it. Mmm it look good.
It just look good!

00:05:39.592 --> 00:05:41.726
(Laughter)

00:05:41.750 --> 00:05:43.651
That's a great arm -- protection!

00:05:43.675 --> 00:05:46.778
That's who we are, but we've exercised
it so much sometimes

00:05:47.255 --> 00:05:48.810
that it has led to abuse.

00:05:50.008 --> 00:05:54.004
It's led to coldness and callousness
and dehumanized us.

00:05:54.941 --> 00:05:56.093
And we've forgotten

00:05:56.117 --> 00:05:57.530
the mantra across this nation

00:05:57.554 --> 00:05:59.624
is to protect and serve.